          "translation": "an orphan",
          "audioUrl": "https://audio.qurancdn.com/wbw/093_006_003.mp3",
          "charType": "word"
        },
        {
          "position": 4,
          "textUthmani": "فَـَٔاوَىٰ",
          "transliteration": "faāwā",
          "translation": "and give shelter",
          "audioUrl": "https://audio.qurancdn.com/wbw/093_006_004.mp3",
          "charType": "word"
        },
        {
          "position": 5,
          "textUthmani": "٦",
          "transliteration": null,
          "translation": "(6)",
          "audioUrl": null,
          "charType": "end"
        }
      ],
      "translation": "Did He not find you an orphan and give [you] refuge?",
      "transliteration": "Alam ya-jidka yateeman fa-aawaa",
      "audioUrl": "https://everyayah.com/data/Alafasy_128kbps/093006.mp3"
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "key": "93:7",
      "textUthmani": "وَوَجَدَكَ ضَآلًّا فَهَدَىٰ",
      "textUthmaniTajweed": "وَوَجَدَكَ ضَآل<tajweed class=ikhafa>اًّ ف</tajweed>َهَدَىٰ <span class=end>٧</span>",
      "textIndopak": "وَوَجَدَكَ ضَآ لًّا فَهَدٰى‏",
      "words": [
        {
          "position": 1,
          "textUthmani": "وَوَجَدَكَ",
          "transliteration": "wawajadaka",
          "translation": "And He found you",
          "audioUrl": "https://audio.qurancdn.com/wbw/093_007_001.mp3",
          "charType": "word"
        },
        {
          "position": 2,
          "textUthmani": "ضَآلًّۭا",
          "transliteration": "ḍāllan",
          "translation": "lost",
          "audioUrl": "https://audio.qurancdn.com/wbw/093_007_002.mp3",
          "charType": "word"
        },
        {
          "position": 3,
          "textUthmani": "فَهَدَىٰ",
          "transliteration": "fahadā",
          "translation": "so He guided",
          "audioUrl": "https://audio.qurancdn.com/wbw/093_007_003.mp3",
          "charType": "word"
        },
        {
          "position": 4,
          "textUthmani": "٧",
          "transliteration": null,
          "translation": "(7)",
          "audioUrl": null,
          "charType": "end"
        }
      ],
      "translation": "And He found you lost and guided [you],",
      "transliteration": "Wa-Wa-jadaka daal-lan fahada",
      "audioUrl": "https://everyayah.com/data/Alafasy_128kbps/093007.mp3"
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "key": "93:8",
      "textUthmani": "وَوَجَدَكَ عَآئِلًا فَأَغْنَىٰ",
